Following are the steps required to make this application work on a linux environment.

1.  Ensure python and its dependecies are installed using the given commands.
apt-get install -y python python-setuptools python-dev build-essential python-pip python-mysqldb

2.  Install and Configure Web Server
Install Python Flask dependency
pip install flask
pip install flask-mysql
Copy app.py or download it from source repository
Configure database credentials and parameters

3. Start Web Server
FLASK_APP=sample.py flask run --host=0.0.0.0

4. Test
Open any browser and type the following URLs
http://<IPaddress>:8080     => Welcome, this a sample web application
http://<IPaddress>:8080/try   => Please clone and try the given sample
